              "content": "Sloyd: Level 5\n☐ View the \"Sloyd Introduction Video\" for an overview of materials and resources used in Sloyd.\n\n☐ Purchase supplies and introduce students to their Sloyd tools (discuss their care and safe use). Organize them so they are easily accessible.\n\n☐ Allow time for loading and viewing videos if available. We recommend teachers preview tutorials and work a model before teaching it.\n\n☐ Gather supplies for the lessons as listed in the materials list of each day's lesson plans."
